[{"id":889616,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"身边同学好多都结婚了，为下一代开始做打算了<br /><br />我想不明白他们是怎么理解结婚这件事的，本来大家都是学生，上了几年班就结婚了就有点突然<br /><br />我的认知仍停留在学生时代，每天的工作任务就和学校里的作业一样（当然我会拿到工资，但是我又不知道这个工资是高是低）然后拿钱租房，吃饭或者去玩，第二天接着上班<br /><br />我想不明白他们的观念是怎么发生转变的，是从小就有理念灌输吗<br /><br />是不是我的智商多少出了点问题","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/889616","replies":146,"created_ts":1666665664,"created":"10:41:04","title":"想不明白人为什么要结婚","author":"Turkestan","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Turkestan","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e4e098b36b0e5b53aba7f8c340412705?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":889587,"node":"汽车","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/car","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960","description":"<p>如题</p>\n<p><img alt=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/28619cab6fb7e3cb4fc75ce9fb2cb614/stheadline/news_res/2021/11/06/782991/i_src_219377799.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/28619cab6fb7e3cb4fc75ce9fb2cb614/stheadline/news_res/2021/11/06/782991/i_src_219377799.jpg\"/></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.automachi.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Subaru-BRZ-31.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.automachi.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Subaru-BRZ-31.jpg</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/889587","replies":137,"created_ts":1666663050,"created":"09:57:30","title":"为什么国内车厂，不愿意做好玩儿的小车","author":"ferock","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ferock","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b903/95f9/61690_mini.png?m=1398964984"},{"id":889602,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1659331259","description":"<p>怎么能这么恶心啊,感觉阈值调的很低很低,几乎有一半几率都会跳淘宝,这个真的是太恶心了啊,哪个运营 /产品经理的案子,用户体验完全就不考虑是吗</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/889602",